# - Try to find the freetype library
# Once done this will define
#
#  FREETYPE_FOUND - system has Freetype
#  FREETYPE_INCLUDE_DIR - the FREETYPE include directory
#  FREETYPE_LIBRARIES - Link these to use FREETYPE
